        {
            "id": 6253959,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電收黑 靠聯發科、鴻海攜PCB股點火 漲144點收復月線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (27) 日持續反彈，最高漲至 27659.06 點，盤中漲勢一度收斂，雖台積電終場收黑，但在聯發科與鴻海領軍下，加上 PCB 族群從上游至下游全面點火，大盤終場漲 144.99 點或 0.53%，以 27554.53 點作收，收復月線，成交量 4916.04 億元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6253959/l/033d90c1a6e9b17f031bba77843596cc.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">無懼台積電收黑，聯發科、鴻海攜PCB撐盤，漲144點收復月線。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察電子權值股今天表現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 跌 5 元或 0.35%，收 1435 元，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 續強，漲逾 3%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 則漲逾 1%，不過台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 小跌 0.32%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 則小漲 0.72%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 大漲逾半根停板。 </p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>PCB 族群今天全面走揚，包括玻纖布、CCL 及載板皆紅通通。亞電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4939:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4939\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4939-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、楠梓電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2316-TW</a>)、瀚宇博 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5469:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5469\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5469-TW</a>) 皆高掛紅燈，德宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5475:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5475\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5475-TW</a>)、高技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5439:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5439\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5439-TW</a>)、建榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5340-TW</a>)、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)、榮科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)、金居 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8358:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8358\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8358-TW</a>)、鉅橡 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8074:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8074\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8074-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，其他如華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)、富喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1815:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1815\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1815-TW</a>)、金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>) 等則有 2 至 3% 漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體類股持續走強，華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 大漲逾半根停板，創見 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，群聯 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8299-TW</a>)、點序 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6485\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6485-TW</a>)、鈺創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5351-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>) 也有超過 2% 漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>總統賴清德昨 (26) 日宣布，明年國防預算將提高至 GDP 的 3.3%，並編列 1.25 兆元的特跌預算，以強化自我防衛能力，激勵軍工股昨天走強，不過僅有 1 天慶祝行情，今天紛紛翻黑下挫。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>軍工股中，中光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5371-TW</a>)、寶一 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8222:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8222\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8222-TW</a>)、晟田 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4541:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4541\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4541-TW</a>)、事欣科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4916:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4916\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4916-TW</a>)、台船 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2208:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2208\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2208-TW</a>)、亞航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2630:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2630\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2630-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板，漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，龍德造船 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6753:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6753\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6753-TW</a>)、攸泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6928:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6928\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6928-TW</a>)、雷虎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8033:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8033\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8033-TW</a>)、長榮航太 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:2645:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2645\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2645-TW</a>) 則有 1 至 2% 的跌幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
